 F\u00e4lldin]]\n}}\n{{Officeholder table\n| order                         = 14\n| image                         = \n| military_rank                 = Rear admiral\n| officeholder                  = [[Bengt Schuback]] \n| officeholder_sort             = Schuback, Bengt\n| born_year                     = 1928\n| died_year                     = 2015\n| title                         = Vice Chief\n| defence_branch                = <!--Navy-->[[File:Marinen vapen bra.svg|50px]]<br>[[Swedish Navy|Navy]]\n| term_start                    = 1977\n| term_end                      = 1978\n| timeinoffice                  = {{age in years|1977|1978}} years\n| ref                           = <ref>{{harvnb|Uddling|Paabo|1992|p=[http://runeberg.org/vemardet/1993/0975.html 975]}}</ref>\n| cabinet                       = [[Thorbj\u00f6rn F\u00e4lldin]]\n}}\n{{Officeholder table\n| order                         = 15\n| image                         = \n| military_rank                 = Major general\n| officeholder                  = [[Bengt Lehander]]\n| officeholder_sort             = Lehander, Bengt\n| born_year                     = 1925\n| died_year                     = 1994\n| title                         = Vice Chief\n| defence_branch                = <!--Air Force-->[[File:Flygvapnet vapen bra.svg|50px]]<br>[[Swedish Air Force|Air Force]]\n| term_start                    = 1978\n| term_end                      = 1982\n| timeinoffice                  = {{age in years|1978|1982}} years\n| ref                           = {{sfn |''Vem \u00e4r det''|1984|p=[http://runeberg.org/vemardet/1985/0643.htm 643]}}\n| cabinet                       = [[Ola Ullsten]]\n| cabinet2                      = [[Thorbj\u00f6rn F\u00e4lldin]]\n}}\n{{Officeholder table\n| order                         = 16\n| image                         = \n| military_rank                 = Major general\n| officeholder                  = [[Lars-Bertil Persson]]\n| officeholder_sort             = Persson, Lars-Bertil