ande colpo: ecco Dany Mota - Associazione Calcio Monza S.p.A.|website=www.monzacalcio.com|language=it|access-date=2020-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200121001037/https://www.monzacalcio.com/news/1623/|archive-date=21 January 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n{{Fs player|no=|pos=FW|nat=ITA|name=[[Lorenzo Petronelli]]|other=at [[ACF Fiorentina Youth Sector|Fiorentina Primavera]] until 30 June 2020}}<ref name=\"violanews.com\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.violanews.com/giovanili/e-intanto-la-fiorentina-prende-un-giovanissimo-attaccante-dalla-juventus/|title=E intanto la Fiorentina prende un giovanissimo attaccante dalla Juventus|first=Redazione|last=VN|access-date=17 August 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190817182129/https://www.violanews.com/giovanili/e-intanto-la-fiorentina-prende-un-giovanissimo-attaccante-dalla-juventus/|archive-date=17 August 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n{{Fs player|no=|pos=FW|nat=CRO|name=[[Marko Pjaca]]|other=at {{flagicon|BEL}} [[R.S.C. Anderlecht|Anderlecht]] until 30 June 2020}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.juvefc.com/official-marko-pjaca-to-anderlecht-on-loan/|title=OFFICIAL: Marko Pjaca to Anderlecht on loan|last=juvefcdotcom|date=2020-01-31|website=Juvefc.com|language=en-GB|access-date=2020-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200131225132/https://www.juvefc.com/official-marko-pjaca-to-anderlecht-on-loan/|archive-date=31 January 2020|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name=\"violanews.com\"/>\n{{Fs player|no=|pos=FW|nat=ITA|name=[[Carmine Sterrantino]]|other=at [[Novara Calcio|Novara]] until 30 June 2020}}<ref name=\"giovanibianconeri.it\"/>\n{{Fs end}}\n\n==Coaching staff==\n[[File:Sarri 2016.jpg|thumb|upright|[[Maurizio Sarri]] is the current head coach of the club]]\n{{updated|10 July 2019}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.juventus.com/en/news/news/2019/the-juventus-first-team-staff-for-2019-20.php|title=The Juventus First Team staff for 2019/20|date=10 July 2019|website=Juventus.com|access-date=10 July 