tephy Mavididi]]|other=at {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Dijon FCO|Dijon]] until 30 June 2020}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ilbianconero.com/a/ufficiale-matheus-pereira-e-mavididi-al-dijon-i-dettagli-59723|title=UFFICIALE: Matheus Pereira e Mavididi al Dijon, i dettagli|website=Juventus News - Ultime Notizie Juve - il BiancoNero|access-date=29 August 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190829152823/https://www.ilbianconero.com/a/ufficiale-matheus-pereira-e-mavididi-al-dijon-i-dettagli-59723|archive-date=29 August 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n{{Fs player|pos=FW|nat=POR|name=[[Dany Mota]]|other=at [[A.C. Monza|Monza]] until 30 June 2020}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.monzacalcio.com/news/1623/|title=Dalla Juventus un grande colpo: ecco Dany Mota - Associazione Calcio Monza S.p.A.|website=www.monzacalcio.com|language=it|access-date=2020-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200121001037/https://www.monzacalcio.com/news/1623/|archive-date=21 January 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n{{Fs player|no=|pos=FW|nat=ITA|name=[[Lorenzo Petronelli]]|other=at [[ACF Fiorentina Youth Sector|Fiorentina Primavera]] until 30 June 2020}}<ref name=\"violanews.com\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.violanews.com/giovanili/e-intanto-la-fiorentina-prende-un-giovanissimo-attaccante-dalla-juventus/|title=E intanto la Fiorentina prende un giovanissimo attaccante dalla Juventus|first=Redazione|last=VN|access-date=17 August 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190817182129/https://www.violanews.com/giovanili/e-intanto-la-fiorentina-prende-un-giovanissimo-attaccante-dalla-juventus/|archive-date=17 August 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n{{Fs player|no=|pos=FW|nat=CRO|name=[[Marko Pjaca]]|other=at {{flagicon|BEL}} [[R.S.C. Anderlecht|Anderlecht]] until 30 June 2020}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.juvefc.com/official-marko-pjaca-to-anderlecht-on-loan/|title=OFFICIAL: Marko Pjaca to Anderlecht on loan|last=juvefcdotcom|date=2020-01-31|website=Juvefc.com|language=en-GB|access-date=2020-