y:21st-century American actresses]]\n[[Category:Actresses from Florida]]\n[[Category:Florida State University alumni]]\n[[Category:American women screenwriters]]\n[[Category:American women film producers]]\n[[Category:American women film directors]]\n[[Category:Screenwriters from Florida]]\n[[Category:Film producers from Florida]]\n", "name_user": "Scott.frymire", "label": "safe", "comment": "Added cross-link to Florida State University College of Motion Picture Arts", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lauren_Miller_Rogen"}
